        "content": "User 2 reposted a post from User 0. Repost content: \ud83d\udea8 BREAKING \u2014 Dubai Real Estate Market Update:\nDubai prime property prices dip 8% QoQ as global risk-off sentiment accelerates. DLD transaction volumes fall 22%. Analysts debate whether this is a healthy correction or the start of a broader downturn.\n\n#DubaiRealEstate #UAEProperty #PropertyMarket. ",
